## File Structure
- `/public/` - Generated static site (deployed to web)
- `/templates/` - Jinja2 HTML templates
- `/scripts/` - Python content generation scripts
- `/data/` - JSON data files
- `/newsletters/` - Generated newsletter HTML
- `/screenshots/` - Playwright screenshots for design feedback

