## Common Tasks
- **Regenerate site:** `python3 scripts/generate_pages.py`
- **Create newsletter:** `python3 scripts/generate_newsletter.py`
- **Update archive:** `python3 scripts/generate_archive.py`
- **Weekly update:** `./run_weekly_update.sh`
- **Deploy:** Auto-deploys on push to main

## Important Notes
- Always regenerate pages after template changes
- Test changes locally before deploying
- Keep design consistent across all pages (index, about, archive, channels)
- Use Playwright screenshots for visual verification
